!ZipArchive.load() works 300ms for rt.jar, while simple

{code}
while (entries.hasMoreElements) {
  entries.nextElement()
}
{code}

works 30ms for rt.jar. Seems like there is something inside !ZipArchive.load() that can be sped up.
